milestones.description: Zaheer Abbas has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for PAK, going past Majid Khan's 3
This is the highest match aggregate (489) involving teams India & Pakistan in ODIs
Vengsarkar and Sandeep Patil's 109-run partnership is IND's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 108 between Sandeep Patil and Malhotra
Zaheer Abbas and Mohsin Khan's 205-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 166 between Majid Khan and Zaheer Abbas
Zaheer Abbas and Mohsin Khan's 205-run partnership is PAK's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 166 between Zaheer Abbas and Majid Khan
